#include<stdio.h>
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int T, N, i;
	long C;
	long ele[10001];
	long sum;
	cin>>T;
	while(T!=0)
	{
	        sum=0;
		cin>>N>>C;
		for(i=0;i<=N-1;i++)
		{
			cin>>ele[i];
			sum = sum + ele[i];
		}
		if(sum<=C)
		cout<<"Yes"<<endl;
		else
		cout<<"No"<<endl;
		T--;
	}
	return 0;
}
